Modifications on some files of Python-2.7.2:

xmipp_setup.py -> Python-2.7.2/setup.py
#XMIPP: disable _curses_panel
disabled_module_list = ['_curses_panel']

xmipp_site.py -> Python-2.7.2/Lib/site.py
##########################################################
    #XMIPP: added some path relative to xmipp_home to the default interpreter search path
    from os.path import join, dirname
    if os.environ.has_key('XMIPP_HOME'):
        xmipp_home = os.environ['XMIPP_HOME']
    else:
        raise Exception("XMIPP_HOME environment variable is not set")
    sys.path += [os.path.join(xmipp_home, dir) for dir in ['lib', 'protocols', 'applications/tests/pythonlib', 'lib/python2.7/site-packages']]
    #XMIPP: This is needed because of nonstandard installation of TCL/TK
    tcl_home = join(xmipp_home, 'external', 'python', 'tcl8.5.10')
    tk_home = join(xmipp_home, 'external', 'python', 'tk8.5.10')
    os.environ['TCL_LIBRARY'] = join(tcl_home, 'library')
    os.environ['TK_LIBRARY'] = join(tk_home, 'library')
    #XMIPP: Add TCL/TK internal libs directory to avoid link to /xmipp/lib/
    os.environ['LD_LIBRARY_PATH'] += ":%s:%s" % (join(tcl_home, 'unix'),  join(tk_home, 'unix'))
#########################################################

Python-2.7.2/Modules/_io/_iomodule.h has to be modified:
